Steps to use this tutorial :

Intall the latest version of ignition-transport. This requires ignition-transport3.

Follow http://ignition-transport.readthedocs.io/en/default/installation/installation.html and install from source, to have the latest version. Before that, you need to setup to accept packages from the packages.osrfoundation.org. ( Read top of the article)

Clone this repo.

Follow instructions on http://ignition-transport.readthedocs.io/en/default/messages/messages.html


Any problem, send a mail. 
You should know how to stalk on git :P
